Package: bayesmendelComparator
Type: Package
Title: Evagene Integration Example - BayesMendel Model Comparator
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A minimal Evagene REST API integration that calls the three
    BayesMendel cancer-risk models (BRCAPRO, MMRpro, PancPRO) for a single
    pedigree and prints a side-by-side comparison.  Distributed as an
    example; not a validated clinical tool.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
